{"tid":1521806,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[仆街婆婆] 婆婆出顏色水的原因","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:53:11.000Z","uid":290573,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"baba972dd4c61a4f79eb979d08b4674fc911334c","tid":1521806,"uid":290573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:53.000Z","msg":"出顏色水的原因並非捉人，而且燒大家的gear，我們要想想如何保存好gear。"},{"pid":"cbd56080c9d7e816a4bd33b6145a15f0c028d3e6","tid":1521806,"uid":314979,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqOQQN5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqOQQN5.gif&h=f1d4c489&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8f015d1ef1f92f757276e6e54f6907c429e6b61","tid":1521806,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"7b41a15aba0cf504f4baa6d65f93383e65655434","tid":1521806,"uid":122623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"唔係for認人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4301280f6997b80aa6e91312f968fdbbfe8c7602","tid":1521806,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eabf53b59d8a3f1c87e904f9a5a826163ceb205c","tid":1521806,"uid":290573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b41a15aba0cf504f4baa6d65f93383e65655434","tid":1521806,"uid":122623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"唔係for認人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:53:11.000Z","msg":"你諗下，既然容易可以用消毒濕紙巾可以搞掂。為何還要出？"}]}